  doi       = "10.2337/diacare.28.12.2939",
  pmid      =  16306558,
  issn      = "0149-5992,1935-5548",
  annote    = "ICEMAN\_REF\_49: Pittas AG, Das SK, Hajduk CL, Golden J, Saltzman
               E, Stark PC, et al. A low-glycemic load diet facilitates greater
